Package org.apache.sis.storage.netcdf

Maps ISO metadata elements from/to the CF-compliant attributes in a NetCDF file.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeNames
    Name of attributes used in the mapping from/to NetCDF metadata to ISO 19115 metadata.
    AttributeNames.Dimension
    Holds the attribute names describing a simple latitude, longitude, and vertical bounding box.

Package org.apache.sis.storage.netcdf Description

Maps ISO metadata elements from/to the CF-compliant attributes in a NetCDF file. The mapping is defined in the following web pages:
  • NetCDF Attribute Convention for Dataset Discovery wiki
  • UnidataDD2MI.xsl file
The NetCDF attributes recognized by this package are listed in the AttributeNamesÂ class.
Since:
0.3 (derived from geotk-3.20)

Defined in the sis-netcdf module (download)
